metadata.name: imperfect checks 1
metadata.description:
this artwork may or may not be perfect or notable

permissionless creation inspired by @jackbutcher ser!

embrace the imperfect you!

It struck me that the Checks inspired by Damien Hirst resemble his perfect dots. While the imperfect version was yet to be made. I got down to working on the meme titled 'imperfect checks' No two checks are the same. Just like each of us is unique.

Embracing imperfection has been one of my biggest learnings in the past 2 years. From imperfect tweets to answers and essays in exams, embracing imperfection has taught me to focus on the progress made through each iteration.

It helped me overcome my fear to express myself. I hope this work inspires the same feeling in you. 

Original Checks by @visualizevalue
